* Chernobyl Siren - SPICE Models (Approximate)

* MP26B / МП26Б
* Approximate LTspice model fitted from family datasheet:
* PNP germanium, hFE ~30..80, ft ~0.5 MHz, noticeable leakage

.model MP26B_REAL PNP(
+ IS=2e-7
+ BF=55
+ BR=8
+ VAF=25
+ IKF=0.015
+ ISE=8e-7
+ NE=1.35
+ ISC=2e-7
+ NC=1.6
+ RB=12
+ RE=1.2
+ RC=1.0
+ CJE=180p
+ VJE=0.18
+ MJE=0.33
+ CJC=55p
+ VJC=0.22
+ MJC=0.33
+ TF=220n
+ TR=8u
+ EG=0.67
+ XTI=2
+ XTB=1.6
)

